# omni-pentest-playbook

Personal pentesting + networking knowledge base.

## Structure

- `0_foundations/` – Networking, ports, TCP/UDP, tcpdump, Wireshark, Linux basics.
- `1_recon/` – DNS, web recon, nmap scanning, wordlists.
- `2_web_app/` – Burp Suite, cookies, sessions, IDOR, fuzzing, bug bounty notes.
- `3_network_pentesting/` – SMB, FTP, SSH, SNMP, common attack flows.
- `4_labs_and_walkthroughs/` – HTB/THM/CTF notes and walkthroughs.
- `5_tools/` – Tool-specific cheatsheets (nmap, Wireshark, Burp, gobuster, etc.).
- `6_scripts/` – Helper scripts for recon, enumeration, sanity checking.
- `7_exam_prep/` – eJPT notes, quizzes, flashcards.
